OL,6,FLucy Letby's father wanted the
OL,7,F"instant dismissal" of two consultants
OL,8,Fwho raised concerns she was
OL,9,Fdeliberately harming babies on a
OL,10,Fhospital neonatal unit, a public
OL,11,Finquiry has heard.
OL,13,FJohn Letby was also said to have
OL,14,F"exerted pressure" via phone calls to
OL,15,Fmembers of staff at the Countess of
OL,16,FChester Hospital.
