OL,3,CLucy Letby's father 'wanted dismissal
OL,4,Cof two consultants who raised concerns'
OL,6,FOne of the people he spoke to was the
OL,7,Fhospital's then HR director who told
OL,8,Fthe Thirlwall Inquiry into the events
OL,9,Fsurrounding Letby's crimes that it was
OL,10,Fthe only time she had spoken to a
OL,11,Frelative of a staff member about an
OL,12,Femployment issue.
OL,14,FHis calls to Sue Hodkinson came weeks
OL,15,Fafter a meeting in December 2016 when
OL,16,FMr Letby and his wife, Sue, stated to
OL,17,Fhospital executives their daughter
OL,18,F"had been to hell and back" after she
OL,19,Fwas moved from the unit five months
OL,20,Fearlier following the concerns
OL,21,Fexpressed by the consultant body.
