OL,3,CLucy Letby's father 'wanted dismissal
OL,4,Cof two consultants who raised concerns'
OL,6,FLetby was said to have felt Dr Stephen
OL,7,FBrearey and Dr Ravi Jayaram had
OL,8,F"orchestrated a campaign" to have her
OL,9,Fremoved amid claims some doctors on
OL,10,Fthe unit referred to her publicly as
OL,11,F"angel of death" and "murderer on the
OL,12,Funit".
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, the inquiry heard Mr Letby
OL,15,Falso told hospital bosses: "The
OL,16,Fbehaviour of those two people, they
OL,17,Fshould be instantly dismissed."
