OL,3,CLucy Letby's father 'wanted dismissal
OL,4,Cof two consultants who raised concerns'
OL,6,FHe also wanted to know what "severity
OL,7,Fof actions" would take place against
OL,8,Fthe two doctors after medical director
OL,9,FIan Harvey was noted to say it was
OL,10,F"inappropriate behaviour".
OL,12,FMr Letby also made numerous phone
OL,13,Fcalls to occupational health nurse
OL,14,FKathryn de Beger, who had been
OL,15,Fassigned to support Letby following
OL,16,Fher redeployment.
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@KO]rD@AOUrD@YO]
