OL,3,CLucy Letby's father 'wanted dismissal
OL,4,Cof two consultants who raised concerns'
OL,6,FGiving evidence, Ms Hodkinson said:
OL,7,F"She described to me how Mr Letby was
OL,8,Fgetting agitated on the phone with
OL,9,Fher, that it was becoming increasingly
OL,10,Fdifficult to manage and she felt very
OL,11,Funcomfortable.
OL,13,F"I felt I needed to support her
OL,14,Fthrough this situation. In fact I
OL,15,Fdon't think I had ever spoken to a
OL,16,Fmember of a family in relation to an
OL,17,Femployment issue. That was the only
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
