OL,3,CLucy Letby's father 'wanted dismissal
OL,4,Cof two consultants who raised concerns'
OL,6,F"And then having the conversation with
OL,7,FMr Letby it was very clear it was a
OL,8,Fvery difficult set of conversations.
OL,10,F"In my view he wanted to express his
OL,11,Fanger towards the ongoing situation
OL,12,Fwith Letby.
OL,14,F"John was placing Kathryn under
OL,15,Fsignificant pressure to have the calls
OL,16,Fescalated to a more senior level.
OL,18,F"In normal circumstances I would not
OL,19,Fhave dealt with a call of this nature
OL,20,For spoken to a staff member's parent.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
