OL,3,CLucy Letby's father 'wanted dismissal
OL,4,Cof two consultants who raised concerns'
OL,6,FBut Letby never returned to the unit
OL,7,Fas the hospital finally called in the
OL,8,Fpolice in May 2017 after previously
OL,9,Fopting to commission a series of
OL,10,Freviews into the increased numbers of
OL,11,Fdeaths in 2015 and 2016.
OL,13,FMs Hodkinson said a "real turning
OL,14,Fpoint" happened on March 15 2017 when
OL,15,FDr Jayaram told her about an incident
OL,16,Fin February 2016 when he had seen
OL,17,FLetby at a baby's cot side and that a
OL,18,Fvalve had moved to a different setting.
OL,26,@uD@UOUvD@FO]
