OL,3,CLucy Letby's father 'wanted dismissal
OL,4,Cof two consultants who raised concerns'
OL,6,FMs Hodkinson said it made her feel
OL,7,F"really, really uncomfortable" and she
OL,8,Fwas "stunned".
OL,10,FShe said: "I didn't think we had
OL,11,Freally looked into some of the aspects
OL,12,Fenough clinically and I have to take
OL,13,Fhis concerns seriously.
OL,15,F"I remember going home at night and I
OL,16,Fwas in tears about it."
OL,18,FShe told the inquiry she believed what
OL,19,FDr Jayaram had told her and informed
OL,20,Ffellow executives the next day.
